      	<h1>NOTICE: On October 30, 2019, GetEducated adopted an amended Privacy Policy, providing as follows:</h1>
      	<p>GetEducated and each Member that provides courses through the GetEducated Site care about the confidentiality and security of your information. This Privacy Policy applies to information that GetEducated collects through the GetEducated Site when you interact with GetEducated, with Members, with other users, and generally with the GetEducated Site.</p>
      	<p>Your information is received and controlled by GetEducated according to this Privacy Policy when you sign up for an GetEducated account or otherwise use the GetEducated Site.</p>
      	<ul>
      		<li>GetEducated is solely and independently responsible for its own privacy practices. No Member is responsible for GetEducated’s privacy practices.</li>
      		<p>If you enroll in a course offered by a Member through the GetEducated Site, information about you and your activity in the course is received and controlled also by that Member as described in this Privacy Policy.</p>
      		<li>Each Member is solely and independently responsible for its own privacy practices. No Member is responsible for another Member’s privacy practices. Also, GetEducated is not responsible for any Member’s privacy practices.</li>
      	</ul>
      	<p>If you do not accept the terms of this Privacy Policy, then please do not access, browse, or register for the GetEducated Site or enroll in any courses. If you choose not to provide certain information required to provide you with various products and services offered on the GetEducated Site, then you may not be able to establish a user account or obtain those products or services.</p>
      	<p>Any version of this Privacy Policy in a language other than English is provided for convenience and you understand and agree that the English language version will control if there is any conflict.</p>

